experience.title: JBA Designs
experience.body: Responsible for drafting and designing floor plans, foundation plans, roof plans, elevations, and electrical plans for custom homes. Designed and maintained customer-facing website, as well as managed on-site NAS solution.

education.title: Bachelor of Science - Computer Science
education.body: Studies included advanced topics regarding computer science such as graph theory, automata, architecture, data structures & algorithms, linear algebra, graphics, database design & administration, and web development. Attended as an honor student. Delivered a thesis regarding graphical tools and methods for teaching young students how to program.

education.title: Associate of Science - Computer Science
education.body: Studies included fundamentals of computer science, computer architecture, physics, and mathematics. Attended as an honor student and a member of Phi Theta Kappa.
